# Keep the build context minimal and avoid leaking secrets/cruft into the image
# (supports ADR-0002 supply-chain hygiene). The build context is the REPO ROOT
# (see docker/Dockerfile). Only ./server is actually needed by the build stage.
.git
.gitignore
.github
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/*.crt
**/id_rsa*
**/secrets*

# IDE / editor cruft
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/*.iml

# Build/output artifacts that must never enter an image (Maven builds inside the
# image from source; host-built target/ would only bloat the context):
**/target
node_modules
dist
build
*.log

# Everything not required by the build stage:
docs
docker
policy
tests
skills
*.md
